In a login method to produce a signed JWT as response use the following:

```java
import com.kapeta.spring.security.provider.JWTCreatorService;
```

To issue tokens based on userId:

```java
SignedJWT signedJWT = jwtCreatorService.createToken(java.lang.String userId);
String token = signedJWT.serialize();
```

